cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about image denoising, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper proposes a deep learning model for image denoising, which involves optimization and training, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) also likely categories. The paper also mentions the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs), which are commonly used in multimedia processing (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
